data.description: Welcome home! Nestled within a charming neighborhood, boasting a spacious layout, this 2 master bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage POOL home with a circle driveway and RV parking space is sure to pique your interest!  As you enter through the front door, spaciousness greets you with an open view to the pool. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the split bedrooms, creating a floor plan that you will love.  The kitchen is the heart of this home with a sprawling breakfast bar offering granite countertops, wood cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances.  This gourmet kitchen is as beautiful as it is functional. The addition of a gas stove adds a touch of sophistication, allowing you to prepare gourmet meals with ease.  The pool area provides the ideal setting for relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're hosting a poolside barbecue with friends or simply enjoying a quiet afternoon swim, this outdoor oasis offers endless opportunities for leisure and enjoyment.  Situated in a centrally located Venice neighborhood, this home offers the perfect location! location! location! With easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as top-rated schools and recreational facilities a short drive to Wellen Park, Venice Island and the wonderful Venice Beaches, you'll have everything you need to live your best Southwest Florida salt life!  Don't miss your chance to make it yours...come see, come sigh and make this home your own!
